member.name: T:AutoCSer.TestCase.StreamPersistenceMemoryDatabase.Game.GameNodeLocalClient
member.summary: local client node
Local client node 本地客户端节点
member.param: Node global keyword 节点全局关键字
A delegate to create a node operation object 创建节点操作对象委托
Log stream persistence in-memory database local client 日志流持久化内存数据库本地客户端
Node index information 节点索引信息

Persistence service node produces success but PersistenceCallbackException when performing a abnormal state node will not operate until the exception is repair and restart the server, If this parameter is set to true, the server node will be automatically deleted and a new node will be recreated after the exception occurs during the call to avoid the situation where the node is unavailable for a long time. The cost is that all historical data will be lost 服务端节点产生持久化成功但是执行异常状态时 PersistenceCallbackException 节点将不可操作直到该异常被修复并重启服务端，该参数设置为 true 则在调用发生该异常以后自动删除该服务端节点并重新创建新节点避免该节点长时间不可使用的情况，代价是历史数据将全部丢失

member.name: T:AutoCSer.TestCase.StreamPersistenceMemoryDatabase.CallbackNodeLocalClient
member.summary: 回调测试节点 local client node
Local client node 本地客户端节点
member.param: Node global keyword 节点全局关键字
A delegate to create a node operation object 创建节点操作对象委托
Log stream persistence in-memory database local client 日志流持久化内存数据库本地客户端
Node index information 节点索引信息

Persistence service node produces success but PersistenceCallbackException when performing a abnormal state node will not operate until the exception is repair and restart the server, If this parameter is set to true, the server node will be automatically deleted and a new node will be recreated after the exception occurs during the call to avoid the situation where the node is unavailable for a long time. The cost is that all historical data will be lost 服务端节点产生持久化成功但是执行异常状态时 PersistenceCallbackException 节点将不可操作直到该异常被修复并重启服务端，该参数设置为 true 则在调用发生该异常以后自动删除该服务端节点并重新创建新节点避免该节点长时间不可使用的情况，代价是历史数据将全部丢失

Persistence service node produces success but PersistenceCallbackException when performing a abnormal state node will not operate until the exception is repair and restart the server, If this parameter is set to true, the server node will be automatically deleted and a new node will be recreated after the exception occurs during the call to avoid the situation where the node is unavailable for a long time. Persistence service node produces success but PersistenceCallbackException when performing a abnormal state node will not operate until the exception is repair and restart the server, If this parameter is set to true, the server node will be automatically deleted and a new node will be recreated after the exception occurs during the call to avoid the situation where the node is unavailable for a long time. The cost is that all historical data will be lost 服务端节点产生持久化成功但是执行异常状态时 PersistenceCallbackException 节点将不可操作直到该异常被修复并重启服务端，该参数设置为 true 则在调用发生该异常以后自动删除该服务端节点并重新创建新节点避免该节点长时间不可使用的情况，代价是历史数据将全部丢失

member.name: T:AutoCSer.TestCase.StreamPersistenceMemoryDatabase.PerformanceSearchTreeDictionaryNodeLocalClient
member.summary: 性能测试二叉搜索树节点接口 local client node
Local client node 本地客户端节点
member.param: Node global keyword 节点全局关键字
A delegate to create a node operation object 创建节点操作对象委托
Log stream persistence in-memory database local client 日志流持久化内存数据库本地客户端
Node index information 节点索引信息

Persistence service node produces success but PersistenceCallbackException when performing a abnormal state node will not operate until the exception is repair and restart the server, If this parameter is set to true, the server node will be automatically deleted and a new node will be recreated after the exception occurs during the call to avoid the situation where the node is unavailable for a long time. The cost is that all historical data will be lost 服务端节点产生持久化成功但是执行异常状态时 PersistenceCallbackException 节点将不可操作直到该异常被修复并重启服务端，该参数设置为 true 则在调用发生该异常以后自动删除该服务端节点并重新创建新节点避免该节点长时间不可使用的情况，代价是历史数据将全部丢失
